Eve Addison, 24, developed a strange swelling in her collarbone after drinking gin and tonic .
But when switching brands failed to help, tests revealed she was suffering Hodgkin Lymphoma - cancer of the lymphatic system .
The most common symptom of Hodgkin lymphoma is one or more painless swellings in the neck, armpit or groin .
This swellings are enlarged lymph nodes - oval-shaped glands that help the body recognise and fight germs .